      "title": "<span id=\"#26310\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">announcement</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>1798年，源自法语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">announcement</i>，源自古法语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">anoncier</i> “宣布，公告”（见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of announce \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/announce\">announce</a>）。或者是由英语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">announce</i> 和 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ment \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ment\">-ment</a> 组成的。在相同的意义上，更早的词是 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">announcing</i>。</p>"
    }
